You can simply ask Alexa to turn on, turn off or dim the lights.There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo. After connecting Alexa to your ENERGIZER SMART products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download the "ENERGIZER SMART" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register an ENERGIZER SMART account in our "ENERGIZER SMART" app;
(3). You need to have some ENERGIZER SMART devices available;
(4). Configure these devices in the ENERGIZER SMART app and change the name for your devices which will be used in "ENERGIZER SMART" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "ENERGIZER SMART" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "ENERGIZER SMART", and you'll be navigated to the ENERGIZER SMART login page;
(9). Input your ENERGIZER SMART account username and password, you'll be redirect to the required page;

You can now enjoy the convenience of voice control on your ENERGIZER SMART devices as follows;
“Alexa, turn on kitchen light"
“Alexa, turn off kitchen light"
“Alexa, dim the livingroom light"
“Alexa, brighten livingroom light"
“Alexa, set the livingroom light to 20 percent"
“Alexa, set bedroom light to Blue"
